1.8 Citing the Program
If you wish to cite the program, you can simply refer to the most
recent release note (Ronquist et al., 2011). This manual should be
cited as an online publication. For more tips on citations, you can
run the citations command in the program, which will give you a
number of other relevant citations for the program and its models
and algorithms.
